section.section:
The articles of conversion shall contain:
The name of the corporation and the address of its principal office before its conversion to a cooperative;
The statute under which the corporation was organized;
A statement that the corporation elects to become a cooperative, nonprofit, membership corporation subject to this subtitle;
The name of the corporation after its conversion to a cooperative;
The address of the principal office of the cooperative and the name and address of its resident agent;
The name and address of each director of the cooperative;
The manner in which members or stockholders of the corporation may or shall become members of the cooperative; and
A statement that the articles are executed in accordance with this subtitle.
